  "common": {
    "name": {
      "zh": "柯尔特 M16A1 5.56x45 突击步枪",
      "en": "Colt M16A1 5.56x45 assault rifle"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "M16A1",
      "en": "M16A1"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "美国柯尔特公司在上世纪 60 年代在原版 AR-15/M-16 基础上进行优化而打造的一款突击步枪，5.56x45 毫米口径。M16A1 在越南战争期间正式装备美军，成为了继 M14 之后的新一代标准军用步枪。相较原版 M16，M16A1 在机匣侧面增设有辅助推机柄，并进行了一系列其他改进以提升步枪在实战中的可靠性。尽管以今天的眼光来看，M16A1 多少已经有些过时了，但在收藏家与枪械爱好者手中，它仍然不失为一件经典藏品，并因可靠耐用、精确度高而广受赞誉。",
      "en": "An American-made 5.56x45mm assault rifle developed by Colt in the late 1960s as an improved variant of the original AR-15/M16 design. The M16A1 became the standard service rifle of the US military during the Vietnam War, featuring a forward assist and other refinements for reliability in harsh conditions. Though considered outdated by modern standards, it remains a durable and accurate weapon prized by collectors and shooters alike."
    },
